%% Evidence: MRA-E002, MRA-E003, MRA-E004, MRA-E006, MRA-E008, MRA-E012, MRA-E013, MRA-E014
flowchart LR
  Auth[Admin auth]
  Rate[Rate limits]
  Locks[Row locks]
  Version[Expected version or state]
  ModerationLock[Moderation lock reasons]
  Projection[Dirty marker and lifecycle sync]
  Audit[Audit log]
  Revalidate[Path revalidation]

  Auth --> Rate
  Rate --> Locks
  Locks --> Version
  Version --> ModerationLock
  ModerationLock --> Projection
  Projection --> Audit
  Audit --> Revalidate
